WEBVTT

00:00.578 --> 00:01.914
Previously on Gotham...

00:02.078 --> 00:03.977
- The Doc, you know 'em?
- Oh, I know The Doc.

00:04.080 --> 00:05.723
Sometimes we search for things

00:05.748 --> 00:07.523
we don't wish to find.
Doc! Doc!

00:07.547 --> 00:10.251
- I enjoy being the queen of Gotham.
- Glad we understand each other.

00:10.275 --> 00:11.808
There are other ways

00:11.833 --> 00:12.999
for me to hurt you.

00:13.125 --> 00:14.938
Something's eating at you,
Jim, and you're not gonna

00:14.962 --> 00:16.711
feel clean till you
get it off your chest.

00:18.113 --> 00:19.146
That's done now.

00:19.459 --> 00:21.058
I'm at Sofia Falcone's.

00:21.160 --> 00:22.526
I just shot and killed the Pyg.

00:22.629 --> 00:24.531
I see Arkham's treating you well.

00:24.556 --> 00:27.308
- Good-bye, Oswald.
- I am held captive,

00:27.333 --> 00:28.444
all my brilliance locked away.

00:28.468 --> 00:30.167
You're still there.

00:30.192 --> 00:31.883
And you're gonna help me
find a way out of here.

00:31.907 --> 00:33.375
- I need a name.
- Ivy Pepper.

00:33.400 --> 00:36.901
- I know Ivy.
- No she's changed, like, a lot.

00:37.243 --> 00:38.254
Called Lazarus Water.

00:38.278 --> 00:39.598
What are you going to do with it?

00:40.141 --> 00:42.250
I'm going to make miracles happen.

00:43.328 --> 00:45.897
Reel it in a little? Or
should I call your keeper?

00:45.922 --> 00:47.303
Call Alfred. He won't answer.

00:47.405 --> 00:49.054
- Why?
- 'Cause I fired him.

00:51.000 --> 00:57.074
